asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Jase "Prophet" Crypto
description:
Born into the roughest neighborhood, Jase struggled on the mean streets. (Hey he was just a wee rabbit!). But with his two brothers, they learned to fight back. More importantly, he learned to always get back up.

He grew up. Met Mrs Crypto. And eventually started their own litter. It was just before his second-born, that he had the oddest dream. This vision portrayed a world, run by cryptocurrency. (Amazingly, it was ALSO his surname!). And despite the world thinking he was ex-Looney Tunes... he invested in this "future".

He had conviction. And just like those early days on the streets, he backed himself. And it all paid off.

Nowadays, Jase definitely enjoys his mansions. (One of several in Auckland, Shanghai, Miami, London and Ibiza). However, he's never forgotten his past. It's what prepared him for the future.

description: Hey fluffies, so nice to meet you! Im a super happy kinda fluf and just love making everyone happy and laugh and love dancing and wybing and having a good time. My parents said they called me delicious because I look like the most extravagant tasty cotton candy. I had a really lucky upbringing as my parents were both super successful entertainers and ended up made their money making the biggest amusement parks in fluf.world, you know, Fluffyland. I work there most of the time just wybing with all the visitors, entertaining, and in my downtime do a lot of charity work to help any fluf in need out there. Im a youth mentor and like to take my mentee flufletts for spins in my lambo and rides at Fluffyland. Otherwise I love to hang out with my friends and enjoy being present, in the now, margin the most of every minute in this bizarre, magical miracle they call life. Nice to meet you, I hope we can hang sometime!
